---
import DocLayout from '../layouts/DocLayout.astro';
---

<DocLayout title="Foundry">
  <h1>🏭 Foundry</h1>
  <p>Documentation platform for human-AI collaborative workflows.</p>
  
  <h2>What is this?</h2>
  <p>
    Foundry renders your markdown docs with rich features — tables, code highlighting, 
    Mermaid diagrams, admonitions — and deploys them to GitHub Pages with public/private 
    access control.
  </p>
  
  <h2>Getting Started</h2>
  <p>This site is built from markdown sources defined in <code>foundry.config.yaml</code>. 
  Navigate the docs using the sidebar.</p>
  
  <h2>Architecture</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>v0.1</strong> — Static site on GitHub Pages (you are here)</li>
    <li><strong>v0.2</strong> — API server with Anvil search, TTS, and annotations</li>
    <li><strong>v0.3</strong> — MCP-first API serving both web UI and AI agents</li>
  </ul>
</DocLayout>
